  archive_name: Hive
  archive_image: {fileID: 21300000, guid: e876d61ad779e7e4daeef6c79f11fd41, type: 3}
  description: A near perfect mimicry of a human except for some strange behavioral
    habits(hordes certain objects, eating strange objects and so on), does not make
    eye contact, and struggles with showing and understanding human emotions.
  risk: 'Risk Level: Unknown'
  risk_bullets: '\u2022 Generally harmless

    \u2022 Can mimic the person''s behavior
    and looks perfectly

    \u2022 Has strange behavioral actions

    \u2022 Lack
    of human emotions and expression

'
  solution: Interact with them normally but limit contact. Do not go near their house
    nor should you accept their invitation. Be polite and just call the nearest I.E.R.F.
    to handle the situation. They will send you a date and before that date you must
    move.
  unlockDay: 2
